The project `WorldwideChat` now compiles successfully.
I have generated a Spoon transformation script in `/workspace/spoon-base-template/src/main/java/github/chains/Main.java` which identifies invocations of `parseEnchantment()` and replaces them with `getEnchant()`. This was necessary because the newer version of `XSeries` (8.6.0) used in the project removed `parseEnchantment()`.

I also handled some minor import issues that arose from the transformation process to ensure a clean build.

You can verify the compilation with:
`cd /workspace/WorldwideChat && mvn clean compile`
